text: Life of Kylie is an American reality television series starring businesswoman and reality star Kylie Jenner and her best friend at the time, Jordyn Woods. The eight-part half-hour series was released on August 6, 2017, on the E! cable network. In the show, Kylie talked about her life and the behind the scenes of her makeup business. ==References== Category:2017 American television series debuts Category:2017 American television series endings Category:American reality television series
